Note: The enjoyable moments of childhood pass by in the
blink of an eye. This game progresses in real time, meaning
that time will continue to move forward. Additionally, time
will also advance with each action taken and each transition
between maps.

Please note that the passage of time during map transitions
may vary depending on the location.

The speed at which time progresses in real time can be
changed with the clock item. Additionally, you can instantly
advance time by using the fun book item.
However, the game balance is based on the normal speed.

Please be careful as changing or advancing the speed of time
without caution may disrupt the game balance. It is
recommended to use such features in subsequent playthroughs
or after understanding the game system. [v0]
